(272, 1, '2018-01-04 22:47:38', '2018-01-04 21:47:38', '<div class=\"wrapper\">\n\nThe Innovative Woman Award goal is to promote Entrepreneurship and the women leading it in all sectors. Women now make up 40 percent of new entrepreneurs in the United States — the highest percentage since 1996, according to the 2016 Kauffman Index of Startup Activity. participating, not only you get a chance to win great prizes to help take your business to the next level but you also get a chance to make a statement about women as business leaders, innovators, job creators, game changers whether it is a the local level or on a global scale.\n<h2 class=\"p-1\">Celebrating women leading innovation in the Los Angeles and Orange County</h2>\n<p class=\"p-1\">The stars have aligned to help trigger the trend as robust ecosystems churn out enterprising females equipped with inspiration, know-how and funding. In recent years, the rate of women entrepreneurs has been growing at a percentage at least double that of their male counterparts.</p>\nChek out the timeline on our home page for more information about the calendar. But right now make sur you <a href=\"https://nakayobenin.com/tudigo/project-sign-up/\"><strong>Submit your project</strong></a>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-344\" src=\"http://nakayobenin.com/tudigo/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/climate-kic-350836-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"785\" height=\"523\" />\n\n</div>', 'The Innovation Women Pitch Competition', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '222-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-04 22:47:38', '2018-01-04 21:47:38', '', 222, 'http://nakayobenin.com/tudigo//2017/12/15/222-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(273, 1, '2017-12-15 18:08:16', '2017-12-15 17:08:16', '<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<p class=\"p-1\">Coup d’Envoi est le résultat de la coopération entre Tudigo, spécialiste du financement participatif local, et Société Générale, un partenaire du développement des entrepreneurs.\r\nNous travaillons à l’accompagnement des initiatives locales qui ont du sens.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"title-2\">ENSEMBLE, FAISONS DÉCOLLER VOS PROJETS.</h2>\r\nL’objectif de Coup d\'Envoi est simple : donner à vos idées les moyens de se concrétiser grâce à l’appui\r\ncommunautaire et financier qu’elles méritent. C’est en unissant tous les efforts que nous ferons battre le cœur des initiatives\r\nlocales.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Le concours', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '222-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-15 18:08:16', '2017-12-15 17:08:16', '', 222, 'http://nakayobenin.com/tudigo//2017/12/15/222-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(274, 1, '2017-12-15 18:09:48', '2017-12-15 17:09:48', '<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<p class=\"p-1\">Coup d\'Envoi is the result of the cooperation between Tudigo, a specialist in local participative financing, and Societe Generale, a partner in the development of entrepreneurs. We work to support local initiatives that make sense.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"p-1\">TOGETHER, MAKE YOUR PROJECTS TAKE OFF.</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p-1\">The objective of Kickoff is simple: to give your ideas the means to be realized thanks to the support Community and financial institutions they deserve. It is by uniting all the efforts that we will make the heart of the initiatives local.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Le concours', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '222-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-15 18:09:48', '2017-12-15 17:09:48', '', 222, 'http://nakayobenin.com/tudigo//2017/12/15/222-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
