g.  Occasionally, guest speakers will also participate periodically to offer educational tips.  Collaboration of like-minded entrepreneurs is oftentimes the most rewarding of the entire incubator experience. We will foster that entrepreneurship is a team sport. <strong>Our third pillar</strong> is Cultivation. We will cultivate our clients using the power of practical education. We will essentially teach them what they do not know during our on-going practitioner based educational certificate programs. We believe that entrepreneurship can be taught.\r\n\r\n<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14.4px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; color: #1d1d1d; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"> </em>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-370\" src=\"http://nakayobenin.com/tudigo/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/photo-3.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Tudigo</h1>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">Tudigo is a local crowdfunding platform that connects local businesses with local investors with Funding , Local visibility , Business community creation.</h5>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'WHO WE ARE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '220-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-22 00:03:46', '2017-12-21 23:03:46', '', 220, 'http://nakayobenin.com/tudigo/2017/12/22/220-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
